    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/860630/extras/b1a5d71442ae104dcd6cd7a88e5cd3ef.poster.avif?t=1771924739\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/860630/extras/b1a5d71442ae104dcd6cd7a88e5cd3ef.webm?t=1771924739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/860630/extras/b1a5d71442ae104dcd6cd7a88e5cd3ef.mp4?t=1771924739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每个故事都有两面性！</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当 <strong>“卢夫特瓦弗王牌” (The Aces of the Luftwaffe)</strong> 开始对美国本土发动进攻时，你被委以重任，领导一支由德国精英飞行员组成的杂牌中队执行他们自己的秘密任务。从百慕大三角的一个秘密基地出发，开启一段充满阴谋与欺骗的史诗般空中冒险，翻开历史的新篇章。这一章节很可能成为广为人知的“美利坚合众国”的最后一章！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/860630/extras/1c3ecd248afa3d5059808c3d77e64b08.avif?t=1771924739\" width=600 height=324 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《卢夫特瓦弗王牌：中队 - 迷雾小队》 (ACES OF THE LUFTWAFFE SQUADRON - NEBELGESCHWADER)</strong> 是一款动作感十足、拥有全程配音叙事的 DLC 战役。体验 25 个全新关卡，击败成群的敌人，并挑战 6 个全新的史诗级 Boss。随着等级提升，通过个人技能树升级中队里的每个独特角色。但不要孤军作战！与多达 3 名好友一起，在史诗般的 4 人本地协作战斗中体验扣人心弦的故事情节。你能胜任这项任务吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/860630/extras/22ed863617fd270ce24f748beb2e6a3d.poster.avif?t=1771924739\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/860630/extras/22ed863617fd270ce24f748beb2e6a3d.webm?t=1771924739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/860630/extras/22ed863617fd270ce24f748beb2e6a3d.mp4?t=1771924739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 动作感十足且伴有爆炸性特效的射击游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 拥有全程配音角色的引人入胜的故事情节</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 支持多达 4 人的史诗级协作多人模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 25 个全新关卡和令人兴奋的任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 6 场全新的壮观 Boss 战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 拥有每位僚机全新独立能力的技能树</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 极具挑战性的成就系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 针对游戏过程和过场动画的创意触感反馈</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 史诗般的电影级管弦乐原声带</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/860630/extras/5354c171a699e4ed2639e6ae039864d8.avif?t=1771924739\" width=400 height=129 /></span></p>",
